(131, 'seller', 1, 'ONE MAN SHOW Ruby Edition 100 ml', 'one-man-show-ruby-edition-100-ml-BmIZKH', '[{\"id\":\"56\",\"position\":1}]', 17, 'pc', 1, 1, '[\"2023-05-31-64775c8d65e3c.png\"]', '2023-05-31-64775c8d66266.png', '1', NULL, 'youtube', NULL, '[]', 0, 'null', '[]', '[]', 0, 2100, 850, '0', 'percent', '30', 'percent', 1, '<p><strong>Jacques Bogart One Man Show Ruby Edition</strong>, A variation on the 1980 release of One Man Show, One Man Show Ruby accents the woody and fresh-spicy scent of the original with a dynamic accord of oriental, green and sweet notes that add profound character to the masculine fragrance. Fresh green apple, orange leaf and lavender introduce the scent first; as the cologne settles on the skin, the refined oriental heart notes emerge, featuring saffron, frankincense and labdanum. The familiar woodsy base takes on a new context, with oud and red cedar joined by rich notes of honey. This 2013 release is highly concentrated, resulting in a potent sillage and a very long-lasting scent &ndash; just a small splash will carry you through the day.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Since its inception in 1975, French-based perfume brand Jacques Bogart has offered high-quality men&rsquo;s colognes to a worldwide audience, seeking to create scents that exemplify masculine elegance and strength of character. Bogart&rsquo;s fragrances all feature powerfully concentrated formulas that last with the wearer for hours.&nbsp;<strong>All our products are 100% original, authentic name brands. We do not sell fake or counterfeit products.</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Top Notes:</strong>&nbsp;Orange leaves, Lavender, Green apple<br />\r\n<strong>Middle Notes:</strong>&nbsp;Saffron, Incense, Labdanum<br />\r\n<strong>Base Notes:</strong>&nbsp;Oud, Red cedarwood, Honey</p>', 0, NULL, '2023-05-31 18:41:17', '2023-05-31 18:43:08', 1, 1, NULL, NULL, '2023-05-31-64775c8d663af.png', NULL, 1, NULL);
